# Trades-Trend: Trading & Investment Blog

> A personal project by Konstantin Gromov. A practical guide to trading in financial markets. Professional analytics, strategies (scalping, algo trading), trading psychology, and education on cryptocurrency and binary options trading.

## Main Sections

- [Home](https://trades-trend.com/)
  > Central hub with the latest updates and access to key tools. Cases, market analysis, trading signals, and live trading in real time.
- [About Me](https://trades-trend.com/about)
  > About Trades-Trend and its author. Learn how Konstantin Gromov helps beginners trade with honest market analysis, AI tools, and practical signal statistics.
- [Articles Catalog](https://trades-trend.com/articles)
  > Full knowledge base and library of educational materials. Proven strategies (Scalping, Price Action), trading psychology, and money management.
- [Live Signals](https://trades-trend.com/live-trading)
  > Archive of trading signals for Binarium and Forex with a 15-minute delay. Analytics for EUR/USD, Bitcoin and crypto assets. Signal hit-rate stats.

